Ricky and I are coming together

27:10.655 --> 27:12.308
right as they're falling apart.

27:13.228 --> 27:14.965
Hey, let me see your ring again.

27:17.138 --> 27:20.208
Isn't it funny how the one person
we thought would be a cheater

27:20.209 --> 27:22.179
