27:23.770 --> 27:25.696
Ricky? Yeah.

27:26.390 --> 27:28.000
Of course, he's not perfect.

27:29.253 --> 27:31.570
But neither am I.

27:33.085 --> 27:34.153
Yeah, it's right down there,

27:34.154 --> 27:35.635
