would want to sleep with you,

28:29.740 --> 28:31.346
I mean, look at you.

28:31.347 --> 28:33.948
Damn. Any guy would want to sleep with you.

28:34.123 --> 28:36.487
You're so good looking, you know that?

28:36.488 --> 28:39.757
And sexy, you are really sexy.

28:40.177 --> 28:43.592
You look all innocent, but hey, you're hot.

28:44.137 --> 28:46.951
