if I took advantage of you.

29:27.145 --> 29:28.284
What?

29:28.285 --> 29:30.076
Unless of course, you maybe
took advantage of me?

29:30.077 --> 29:34.438
Oh, no, no, no, no one
took advantage of anyone.

29:34.439 --> 29:35.953
You knew what you were doing.

29:35.954 --> 29:37.907
I already told you, you were pretty good,

29:37.908 --> 29:40.728
