30:17.236 --> 30:20.027
It's none of his business.
It's just me being me.

30:20.454 --> 30:22.288
Or, the old me.

30:22.964 --> 30:25.966
There's a new me now.
I've changed since last week.

30:26.106 --> 30:29.490
It's been a long time
coming, but I've changed.

30:31.033 --> 30:35.142
Yeah, I met someone and I'm going
