30:39.943 --> 30:42.294
You met someone in the last
week, after the party?

30:42.295 --> 30:44.688
No, it's that guy that I
came to the party with.

30:44.689 --> 30:45.920
You came there with someone?

30:45.921 --> 30:47.846
