to either of us, all right?

31:47.570 --> 31:48.937
Not all right.

31:49.014 --> 31:51.997
And I'm not so upset with
you as I am with Henry.

31:52.145 --> 31:54.479
Who you're with is your
business, I suppose,

31:54.480 --> 31:55.942
