31:55.943 --> 31:58.372
Best friends are hard to come
by, you should forgive him.

31:58.373 --> 32:00.085
Did Christ forgive Judas?

32:00.086 --> 32:01.309
I think he did.

32:01.459 --> 32:03.130
Really? Yeah.

32:03.265 --> 32:05.792
