32:33.724 --> 32:35.378
Apparently, you don't
know right from wrong.

32:35.379 --> 32:37.226
Leave Henry alone, he made a mistake

32:37.227 --> 32:38.827
and he feels badly about it.

32:38.828 --> 32:40.850
It doesn't matter how
badly he feels about it,

32:40.851 --> 32:42.090
