37:17.616 --> 37:19.561
maybe you could think about seeing me.

37:20.280 --> 37:22.308
Maybe we could give it just one more shot.

37:23.016 --> 37:25.694
Not tonight, not this week,
maybe not even this summer,

37:25.695 --> 37:30.067
but when you're ready to go out again.
Think about it.

37:30.993 --> 37:32.314
Please go out with me.

37:33.742 --> 37:35.841
